description.p:
Numbered clause 25. The electrical safety device of any of clauses 20 to 24 wherein the isolation unit comprises a processor and one or more local sensors. the one or more local sensors comprising one or more of:
a thermal sensor;
a smoke and/or gas sensor;
a carbon monoxide sensor;
a moisture and/or water sensor;
a current sensor; wherein the isolation unit is configured restrict a flow of water, gas or electricity when the processor determines that a parameter sensed by a local sensor exceeds a predetermined threshold.
